1
00:00:53,930 --> 00:00:54,504
Kaew...

2
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:56,455
are you actually trying to practice,

3
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:58,006
or are you really trying to kill me here?

4
00:01:02,620 --> 00:01:05,563
If I don't practice for real, how am I ever going to get any good?

5
00:01:07,130 --> 00:01:07,981
I yield,

6
00:01:08,620 --> 00:01:09,606
With skills like yours,

7
00:01:10,369 --> 00:01:13,316
if you were a man, you’d probably be a high-ranking soldier by now.

8
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:17,649
And what’s wrong with being a woman?

9
00:01:22,541 --> 00:01:23,130
Dad!

10
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,193
Dad!

11
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,129
Dad,

12
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:38,036
I told you to call for me if you needed anything.

13
00:01:40,676 --> 00:01:42,313
I was just going to grab my medicine.

14
00:01:43,930 --> 00:01:44,966
I'll go get it for you.

15
00:02:21,170 --> 00:02:22,086
Are you feeling any better?

16
00:02:26,664 --> 00:02:27,809
Please get some rest, Dad.

17
00:02:49,618 --> 00:02:50,843
Rest up, okay?

18
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,467
Out of medicine again?

19
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:24,867
Yeah...

20
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:27,889
I shouldn't be gone too long.

21
00:03:58,460 --> 00:03:59,827
Hey! Hurry it up!

22
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:01,003
Yeahhh

23
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:05,120
Hey... you look more handsome with that mustache!

24
00:04:05,144 --> 00:04:07,500
If you're not going to help, don't mess with me.

25
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:25,403
I didn't mean to.

26
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,369
I'm sorry.

27
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:33,883
It's alright.

28
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,236
- Are you hurt anywhere?
- Come here!

29
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:38,996
Where are we going?

30
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,083
if...

31
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:18,849
Don't speak.

32
00:05:24,498 --> 00:05:26,490
You smell so strongly of jasmine,

33
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,486
they'll catch your scent.

34
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:43,926
Then... who are you running away from?

35
00:05:47,050 --> 00:05:48,116
Did you find her?

36
00:05:48,141 --> 00:05:48,929
I didn't see her either.

37
00:05:48,941 --> 00:05:49,913
Let's go look over that way then.

38
00:05:52,730 --> 00:05:53,600
No,

39
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,778
I was just running in a hurry.

40
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:02,935
Are you well-acquainted with this market?

41
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,738
I know it well enough.

42
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,030
Why do you ask?

43
00:06:09,210 --> 00:06:11,815
In that case, please lead the way for me.

44
00:06:11,852 --> 00:06:13,433
I have never visited a market before.

45
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,326
Do you mean...

46
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:19,403
you have never visited this market?

47
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,529
I have never visited any market at all.

48
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,538
I happen to be heading just up ahead anyway.

49
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,393
You may come with me.

50
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,716
What is this?

51
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:53,987
Sweet Mung Bean Paste

52
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:56,123
Is it edible?

53
00:06:58,086 --> 00:06:58,972
Well, it is sweet.

54
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,990
And what kind of curry is this?

55
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:13,113
Red curry.

56
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,612
Is it spicy?

57
00:07:16,530 --> 00:07:17,181
Very.

58
00:07:19,673 --> 00:07:21,670
Then I probably won't like it.

59
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:27,680
And what about this?

60
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:28,449
Jackfruit.

61
00:07:29,290 --> 00:07:30,793
I haven't even asked yet.

62
00:07:31,550 --> 00:07:33,766
Well, you ask about everything you see.

63
00:07:34,049 --> 00:07:36,701
And you answer everything I ask.

64
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,683
How truly generous of you.

65
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:40,110
Make way, make way!

66
00:07:40,135 --> 00:07:41,987
Move aside, move aside! Please make way!

67
00:07:51,550 --> 00:07:55,366
Do you always like pulling people close to you like this?

68
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:03,772
I was merely making sure you wouldn't get hurt.

69
00:08:13,470 --> 00:08:15,827
The market is more fun than I thought.

70
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,384
But for some people,

71
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,178
it is not like that at all.

72
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:30,923
I must go now.

73
00:08:31,490 --> 00:08:32,701
My name is Rinkham.

74
00:08:32,910 --> 00:08:34,430
And what is yours?

75
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,276
My name is Kaewke...

76
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:39,341
My name is Kaew.

77
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:44,603
It was a pleasure meeting you, Kaew.

78
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,984
I hope we meet again.

79
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:25,200
Ruby body chain...

80
00:09:28,123 --> 00:09:29,944
You are certainly no ordinary servant.

81
00:09:33,409 --> 00:09:35,400
Which lord's household do you belong to, I wonder?
